OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,FThe full list of candidates for
OL,7,FJersey's upcoming general election has
OL,8,Fbeen announced.
OL,10,F92 candidates will be competing for 49
OL,11,FSenator, Constable, and Deputy
OL,12,Fpositions in the island's States
OL,13,FAssembly.
OL,15,FUltimately, voters will choose 37
OL,16,FDeputies to represent nine electoral
OL,17,Fconstituencies, 9 Senators to
OL,18,Frepresent island-wide issues, and 12
OL,19,FConstables to represent each of the
OL,20,Fisland's 12 parishes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
