OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,FBut how does the initial line-up
OL,7,Fcompare to previous years, and
OL,8,Fprevious Assemblies?
OL,10,FITV News breaks down the demography of
OL,11,Fthis year's candidates...
OL,13,FCompared to previous elections
OL,15,FA total of 92 candidates are standing
OL,16,Fin this year's election.
OL,18,FThis compares very similarly to the
OL,19,Ftwo previous elections: in 2022 there
OL,20,Fwere 92 candidates, and in 2018 there
OL,21,Fwere 91.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
