OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,FSo the position of Constable will be
OL,7,Fmore highly-contested than in previous
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FA total of 29 women and 63 men are
OL,11,Fstanding for election - making 32.5%
OL,12,Fof this year's candidates female.
OL,14,FThis is a slight drop from 2022's
OL,15,Fgeneral election, where 32 of the 92
OL,16,Fcandidates were women.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
