OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,F20 of those standing for Deputy are
OL,7,Falready sitting Deputies; 18 are new;
OL,8,Fseven served as Deputies under
OL,9,Fprevious Assemblies; and seven have
OL,10,Fstood for election on previous
OL,11,Foccasions.
OL,13,FEight of the people standing to be
OL,14,FSenator are current Deputies; three of
OL,15,Fthem have served previous terms as
OL,16,FStates members; and two of them were
OL,17,Fprevious candidates.
OL,19,FFour of them have never stood for
OL,20,Felection before.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
