OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,FNine of the people standing for
OL,7,FConstable are currently serving as
OL,8,FConstables, and four of them are
OL,9,Fcurrent Deputies.
OL,11,FTwo of them were past States members;
OL,12,Ffour were candidates in previous
OL,13,Fyears; and four have never previously
OL,14,Fstood for election.
OL,16,FIndependents
OL,18,F74 candidates are independent and are
OL,19,Fnot affiliated with any political
OL,20,Fparty.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
