OL,3,CFirst look: how do this year's
OL,4,Celection candidates compare?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 18 belong to one of two
OL,7,Fpolitical parties - People First are
OL,8,Fnominating two candidates, and Reform
OL,9,FJersey are nominating 16.
OL,11,FSome candidates are also affiliated
OL,12,Fwith the political movement 'Value
OL,13,FJersey', although this is not a
OL,14,Fpolitical party and this will not
OL,15,Fappear on the ballot paper.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
